程序包 org.springframework.lang

Annotations indicating the use of core Java/JDK API beyond the API level of JDK 6 update 18.

请参阅: 说明

  • 注释类型概要 
    注释类型 说明
    UsesJava7 已过时
    UsesJava8 已过时
    UsesSunHttpServer
    Indicates that the annotated element uses the Http Server available in com.sun.* classes, which is only available on a Sun/Oracle JVM.
    UsesSunMisc
    Indicates that the annotated element uses an API from the sun.misc package.

程序包org.springframework.lang的说明

Annotations indicating the use of core Java/JDK API beyond the API level of JDK 6 update 18. Used descriptively within the framework codebase; validated by Animal Sniffer at build time.
